	to an empty list.
	(getgrnam_r): Ditto.
	(app_gr): New static struct to store group data propagated to the
	calling application via getgrgid/getgrnam.
	(getgr_cp): Fill app_gr and return pointer to app_gr.g.
	(getgrgid32): Call getgr_cp.
	(getgrnam32): Ditto.
